title: Scala & Kolacny Brothers - Studio Discography 2002-2011 - MP
description:
Scala is a Belgian women's choir conducted by Stijn Kolacny and arranged and accompanied by Steven Kolacny on the piano. - Wikipedia

=====

This collection includes (as near as I can discern) every studio track from 2002 to 2011, both albums and singles. There are several tracks released on two albums but there were minor variations between the files from each album, so I would have to compare side by side to tell if they are truly duplicate tracks.

I claim no credit for this upload. I found it already healthy and well-seeded in the Distributed Hash Table (as viewed by btdigg).

Bitrates:
Albums, 320KBps (Except 2011 - Self Titled UK, 256KBps)
Singles, 192KBps

Thanks to the original uploader, and all the peers who continue seeding.
